#: src/Dialogs/dlgGestureHelp.cpp:16
msgid ""
"# Gesture Navigation\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar supports touch gestures on the map:\n"
"\n"
"- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Swipe Up** (U): Zoom in\n"
"- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Swipe Down** (D): Zoom out\n"
"- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Swipe Right** (R): Previous screen "
"mode\n"
"- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Swipe Left** (L): Next screen mode\n"
"- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Up-Down** (UD): Auto zoom\n"
"- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Menu\n"
"- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Down-Right** (DR): Waypoint details\n"
"- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Down-Left** (DL): Alternates\n"
"- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Right-Down** (RD): Task manager\n"
"- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Up-Right-Down** (URD): Analysis\n"
"- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Left-Down-Right** (LDR): Checklist\n"
"- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Up-Right-Down-Left** (URDL): Pan "
"mode\n"
"- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Left-Down-Right-Down-Left** "
"(LDRDL): Status\n"
"- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Up-Left-Down-Right** (ULDR): Quick "
"menu\n"
"\n"
"Long-press on the map to enter Pan mode. Tap while in Pan mode to see nearby "
"waypoints."
msgstr ""
"# Navigare prin gesturi\n"
"\n"
"XCSoar acceptă gesturi tactile pe hartă:\n"
"\n"
"- ![U](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UP) **Glisați în sus** (U): măriți\n"
"- ![D](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DOWN) **Glisează în jos** (D): micșorează\n"
"- ![R](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RIGHT) **Glisează spre dreapta** (R): Mod ecran "
"anterior\n"
"- ![L](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LEFT) **Glisați spre stânga** (L): Următorul mod "
"de ecran\n"
"- ![UD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_UD) **Sus-Jos** (UD): Zoom automat\n"
"- ![DU](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DU) **Down-Up** (DU): Meniu\n"
"- ![DR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DR) **Jos-Dreapta** (DR): detalii waypoint\n"
"- ![DL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_DL) **Jos-Stânga** (DL): Alternative\n"
"- ![RD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_RD) **Dreapta-jos** (RD): Manager de "
"activități\n"
"- ![URD](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URD) **Sus-Dreapta-Jos** (URD): Analiză\n"
"- ![LDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDR) **Stânga-Jos-Dreapta** (LDR): Lista de "
"verificare\n"
"- ![URDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_URDL) **Sus-Dreapta-Jos-Stânga** (URDL): "
"modul Pan\n"
"- ![LDRDL](resource:IDB_GESTURE_LDRDL) **Stânga-Jos-Dreapta-Jos-Stânga** "
"(LDRDL): Stare\n"
"- ![ULDR](resource:IDB_GESTURE_ULDR) **Sus-Stânga-Jos-Dreapta** (ULDR): "
"Meniu rapid\n"
"\n"
"Apăsați lung pe hartă pentru a intra în modul Pan. Atingeți în modul Pan "
"pentru a vedea punctele de referință din apropiere."

